---
title: RetailForge — Semantic Search & Action Data Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Shopper
    participant FE as Next.js + CopilotKit
    participant RT as Root Concierge (ADK)
    participant SP as Specialist Agent
    participant EM as Gemini Embeddings
    participant TB as MCP Toolbox
    participant DB as MongoDB Atlas

    U->>FE: "Find a waterproof jacket under $100"
    FE->>RT: AG-UI event (SSE)
    RT->>SP: transfer_to_agent (ProductAdvisor)
    SP->>EM: embed query (gemini-embedding-001, 3072-d)
    EM-->>SP: query vector
    SP->>TB: find-similar-products(vector, filters)
    TB->>DB: $vectorSearch on products.embedding
    DB-->>TB: top-k matches + scores
    TB-->>SP: ranked products
    SP-->>FE: stream generative-UI product cards
    FE-->>U: rich result + "Add to Bag"

    Note over SP,DB: Writes (create order, decrement<br/>inventory, refund) flow the same path —<br/>only through declared Toolbox tools.
